Use the standard library
This is how to intersperse of numbers and delimeter:
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this numbers's length times:
      When i is more than 0, then:
         Add result to delimeter
      End when
      Add result to item i in numbers
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is result
Now you know

>>> intersperse of [] and 4
[]
>>> intersperse of [1, 2, 3] and 4
[1, 4, 2, 4, 3]
>>> intersperse of [] and 7
[]